   2:../main.c     ****  * main.c — merged SCUD (RS485) + Morelle (CAN) BMS monitor
   3:../main.c     ****  *
   4:../main.c     ****  * Every 2 seconds:
   5:../main.c     ****  *   1. Poll SCUD BMS over RS485 (USIC1_CH0, P2.14/P2.15 @ 115200 8N1)
   6:../main.c     ****  *      via auto-direction transceiver (THVD1406DR).
   7:../main.c     ****  *   2. Poll Morelle BMS over CAN Node 0 (P2.0 TX / P14.3 RX @ 250 kbps,
   8:../main.c     ****  *      extended 29-bit IDs) via on-board IFX1051LE transceiver.
   9:../main.c     ****  *
  10:../main.c     ****  * Either BMS may be absent — poll failures are printed but do not stop the loop.
  11:../main.c     ****  */
